arStrings.szText: Complete the trial of the Spiritborn
I feel the call of the spirits. I'm being compelled to find someone who can guide me.
An emissary of the spiritborn wants me to participate in something called the Sacred Hunt. This will be dangerous but I feel a yearning at my very core to learn what it means to be spiritborn.
I've been asked to join Tarka the Emissary to investigate an unusual killing. He thinks it's the start of my 'Sacred Hunt,' but I'm skeptical - it could be just coincidence.
Find Tarka the Emissary in Central Plateau
I've been asked to join Tarka the Emissary to investigate an unusual killing. He thinks it's the start of my 'Sacred Hunt,' but I'm skeptical - it could be just coincidence.

Whatever created that bloody carnage in the Central Plateau was not natural. The supernatural is all around us, but something is different about this - it feels connected to me. I must meet Tarka at Hakan's Oasis so we can track the perpetrator down.
Tarka doesn't seem to be Hakan's Oasis, but there is a survivor of an attack here. They are barely clinging to life, but perhaps they know what did this to them and where Tarka went?
Help Tarka the Emissary Open the Portal
In haste, Tarka made south for a place near the river. Apparently the source of this carnage is nearby. I'm not sure I fully understand it all yet, but this sacred hunt is mine.

We've found the scene of fresh kills; corpses, limbs, other body parts, still warm pools of blood litter the site. The stench of death hangs heavy in the air. Whatever did this, we just missed it, but we're close now.
